    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それではっ\n次のコーナー、張り切っていってみよう！",
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！\n違う違う、この台詞MCさんのだ～！！",
      "startTime": 7.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8233.333333400002,
          "startTime": 15.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　立ち位置も違う……？\nわー！　すみませ……わわっ！",
      "startTime": 13.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "いたた……あっ、だ、大丈夫です！\nき、鍛えてるんで！　ムッキムキなんで！",
      "startTime": 19.999998347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、全く大丈夫じゃないな……\nなるほど、これは俺が呼ばれる訳だ",
      "startTime": 27.0333316803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、一旦休憩ですか？\nは、はい、分かりました……",
      "startTime": 33.973150142,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4526.849857999999,
          "startTime": 38.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "うう……、空回っちゃった……えぇ！？\n{user}さん！？　なぜここに！？",
      "startTime": 42.273150142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "全部、見られちゃいましたか……？",
      "startTime": 45.1064903419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、愛\nとりあえず楽屋に戻ろうか",
      "startTime": 50.9000075023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "はいぃ……",
      "startTime": 53.016492637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "転んでいたみたいだけど、大丈夫か？\n怪我とかしてないよな？",
      "startTime": 59.5333398183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫です！　順調ですよ！\nむしろ番組的に美味しいって褒められちゃいました！",
      "startTime": 64.4505489985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "この調子で頑張ります！\n任せて下さい！",
      "startTime": 69.6172156651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん良くして下さいますし\nおかげで大盛り上がりですよ～、あはは……",
      "startTime": 73.2505489985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "盛り上がってるっていうより\n必死にフォローされてるように見えたんだが",
      "startTime": 78.4000049591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "た、たまたまです！\n大丈夫です！",
      "startTime": 82.9792108694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どうだろうな……\n愛、お昼のお弁当は何を食べたんだ？",
      "startTime": 86.5000049591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "任せて下さい！",
      "startTime": 89.8705500919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……今日はなんの仕事だっけ？",
      "startTime": 92.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "小美山愛です！",
      "startTime": 94.8523645876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "マズイな。これは……重症だぞ\n愛、一度深呼吸しようか。はい吸って",
      "startTime": 101.933340327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "深呼吸ですね！？　得意です！\nすぅ～！",
      "startTime": 108.7871716815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "息止めて\n十秒キープ！",
      "startTime": 111.833340327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "いち！　に！　さん！\nはっ……息吐いちゃいました",
      "startTime": 116.6085769334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "声に出す必要はなかったんだが\nとりあえず、落ち着いたみたいだな",
      "startTime": 124.1333398183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "あ……す、すみません……私……\n本当は撮影の最初からずっとあんな感じで……",
      "startTime": 131.7717285314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "気合いを入れて台本を1000回読んで来たんですけど\n他の人の台詞まで全部そのまま喋っちゃって",
      "startTime": 139.7717356521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai019.m4a",
      "text": "大御所の方に……そんな訳ないやろ！　とか\n元気よくツッコミを入れちゃったりして……",
      "startTime": 147.5384023188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（それは……後で頭を下げに行かないとだな）",
      "startTime": 150.4384013015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_02-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "後、こころが『漫画の可愛いセリフ100選』の\n台詞をこっそり練習してることを喋ってしまって",
      "startTime": 158.8487413087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
